<paragraph id="A2D9E1AEFE317F05D52872D2590DAE4B" pageId="9" pageNumber="24">1 M holotype (FKCP), Metahara (approx. 8.900°, 39.900°), Oromia, Ethiopia. Paratypes: 34 M, 34 F, 36 juv. (FKCP), all from the same locality; 1 M (FKCP), Dire Dawa, Ethiopia.</paragraph>
